Class UserInvalidPasswordException

java.lang.Object

java.lang.Exception
java.lang.RuntimeException
com.group6.hms.app.managers.auth.UserInvalidPasswordException
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class UserInvalidPasswordException extends RuntimeException
The UserInvalidPasswordException class is a custom exception that is thrown when a user's password does not meet the required complexity criteria, such as length and character requirements.
